# Local secrets for the Cloudflare dev runtime (used by `wrangler dev` and the
# OpenNext preview). Copy this file to `.dev.vars` and fill in real values.
# `.dev.vars` is gitignored and must never be committed.
#
# For plain `next dev`, the same variables can instead be placed in `.env.local`.

# GitHub personal access token. Used ONLY server-side (Route Handlers) to
# authenticate calls to the GitHub API. A token raises the API rate limit and is
# never exposed to the browser. A fine-grained token with public read access is
# sufficient for searching public repositories.
GITHUB_TOKEN=""

# Optional: only needed if you use Upstash instead of Cloudflare KV for rate
# limiting.
# UPSTASH_REDIS_REST_URL=""
# UPSTASH_REDIS_REST_TOKEN=""
